<subSubSection id="532F9ECCD122779F3E26D51A6DB761A1" pageId="null" pageNumber="847" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="6BC81920CF959CE60A0C4D85AB1D3E50" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Graues Bruchkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="DFA2C56C4FE18FD33DE4E9B83679369A" pageId="null" pageNumber="847" type="description">
<paragraph id="B6F0C22FECC30BC5379F189BF64B6D07" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="C20B4C2CB76D3B9591070ADA57E89955" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Herniaria" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="847" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis id="DA1817A9FACCB19499BCFDC50EA9FCBD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">H. alpina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 3) durch folgende Merkmale: Gelegentlich aufsteigend; 
<emphasis id="F03E2B707F98B94C232AEB797D9C1017" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">
<normalizedToken id="9C13320A6AD613306FD438B287008D1B" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
3-12 mm lang, 3-5mal so lang wie breit, dicht behaart
</emphasis>
(Haare bis 0,5 mm lang); 
<emphasis id="85419FD08DD73EB8366BC728CE2C8C5E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">
<normalizedToken id="D7697EA523D9D394708B2964B1B951D5" originalValue="Nebenblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Nebenblaetter</normalizedToken>
1,5-3 mm lang;
</emphasis>
freie 
<normalizedToken id="EAD32A9986E20EE11C1C9354650509F5" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
dicht behaart. - 
<normalizedToken id="6F7ACCB55A68A5A82DA58926997529C0" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B36AEBAF07E92200B1233C2319025C4F" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">
<emphasis id="1097FC512E8C8C937E1DFB988CF5E8B0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="299C75CDD45BE878F30F1DFE6CE54323" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">
<emphasis id="60049042BCBD138DE3714CF0BB5A0D13" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">
<pageBreakToken id="DA0A7E334543F1CB42DE2CB6C6A11F4B" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Standort</pageBreakToken>
.
</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Offene, trockene, sandige und steinige 
<normalizedToken id="80FEA3BD8EE2663C1F2AEE4F9DBA5A54" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. 
<normalizedToken id="9CB208B1873580962A7A79584A72E0EA" originalValue="Felshänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Felshaenge</normalizedToken>
, sandige 
<normalizedToken id="13A205049A6A72916D8E81432B031103" originalValue="Plätze" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Plaetze</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="E2BAF11973D65490B9EA079CF6D407D5" originalValue="Wegränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Wegraender</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="12DE75E9387E7D281A8A836D1338BDC1" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">
<emphasis id="4DB5F31113F13391D13923F9DE41CF3C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="36415333C543D12E65D56B497F00D7EA" originalValue="Südeuropa" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Suedeuropa</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="D54F91501721FA94EC07AB639BD1DDA1" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Mainz, Alpen, 
<normalizedToken id="BCCC23ECD32A74CDEB3BC7151089A90B" originalValue="Südrußland" pageId="null" pageNumber="847">Suedrussland</normalizedToken>
; Kleinasien, Syrien, Persien; Algerien. - Im Gebiet: Savoyen (Maurienne, Tarentaise).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
